title: Masterpiece Theatre: We've Created Our Own Scripts For Keity's Life Redo!
description:
It's known that women are taken advantage of at mechanic shops, and it just happened to one of us. Not once but twice, our producer Keity was disrespected at a tire shop last week, and she wants a redo. This time, she wants Moe, Kristin, and K. Lee to help her out. You won't believe what happened!
